<P ALIGN=CENTER STYLE="margin-top: 0.42cm; margin-bottom: 0cm"><FONT SIZE=4 STYLE="font-size: 16pt"><B>Instructions
for Authors of SBC Conferences Papers and Abstracts<A CLASS="sdfootnoteanc" NAME="sdfootnote1anc" HREF="#sdfootnote1sym" SDFIXED><SUP>*</SUP></A></B></FONT></P>
<P ALIGN=CENTER STYLE="margin-top: 0.42cm; margin-bottom: 0cm; page-break-before: auto">
<B>Luciana P. Nedel<SUP>1</SUP>, Rafael H. Bordini<SUP>2</SUP>,
Fl&aacute;vio Rech Wagner<SUP>1</SUP>, Jomi F. H&uuml;bner<SUP>3</SUP></B></P>
<P ALIGN=CENTER STYLE="margin-top: 0.42cm; margin-bottom: 0cm; page-break-before: auto">
<SUP>1</SUP>Instituto de Inform&aacute;tica &ndash; Universidade
